divs: Sighting Detailson rolling road in baltimore county saw many cars on road with people out of cars looking towards sky. stopped and looked saw a cigar shaped oblect looked like a jet with no wings. saw many other small lights going in different direction near by. had windows down side and could see figures looking out. craft made a soft sound kind of like an air sound. it tilted a little and then shot off. everyone there just shrugged their shoulders and got in and drove off not sure if this is correct date but a lot of other people saw it too
